OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of murdering
OL,4,Cpensioner 'motivated by conflict in
OL,5,CGaza'
OL,7,FA Moroccan asylum seeker told police
OL,8,Fhe knifed a pensioner to death in the
OL,9,Fstreet and stabbed a Christian convert
OL,10,Fout of "revenge" for Israel killing
OL,11,Fchildren in the Palestinian conflict,
OL,12,Fa court heard.
OL,14,FAlid Ahmed's actions, the week after
OL,15,Fthe Hamas attacks, were motivated by
OL,16,F"the conflict in Gaza and to further
OL,17,Fhis desire that Palestine would be
OL,18,Ffree from the Zionists", Teesside
OL,19,FCrown Court was told.
