OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F426A1712933602
OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of murdering
OL,4,Cpensioner 'motivated by conflict in
OL,5,CGaza'
OL,7,FHe denies murdering Terence Carney,
OL,8,F70, in Hartlepool town centre, as well
OL,9,Fas the attempted murder of his
OL,10,Fhousemate Javed Nouri, 31, and
OL,11,Fassaulting two female police officers
OL,12,Fwho had interviewed him after his
OL,13,Farrest.
OL,15,FJonathan Sandiford KC, prosecuting,
OL,16,Fsaid Alid armed himself with two
OL,17,Fknives in the early hours of 15
OL,18,FOctober when he attacked Mr Nouri, who
OL,19,Fwas asleep, at their shared house in
OL,20,FWharton Terrace, Hartlepool.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/18
