OL,3,CAsylum seeker accused of murdering
OL,4,Cpensioner 'motivated by conflict in
OL,5,CGaza'
OL,7,FAlid shouted "Allahu Akbar", meaning
OL,8,F"God is great", as he stabbed sleeping
OL,9,FMr Nouri in the chest, before he went
OL,10,Fon to fatally stab Mr Carney, who was
OL,11,Fout walking in the town centre.
OL,13,FHe had initially thought Mr Nouri was
OL,14,Fa Muslim, but was angered when he
OL,15,Frealised he was attending church and
OL,16,Fhad converted to Christianity.
OL,18,FMr Nouri and two other housemates,
OL,19,Falso asylum seekers, formed the view
OL,20,Fthat Alid followed an extreme version
OL,21,Fof Islam, the court heard.
