OL,7,FMr Nouri complained to housing bosses
OL,8,Fand the police about Alid, but days
OL,9,Fbefore the attack, an officer told him
OL,10,Fno offence had been committed.
OL,12,FMr Sandiford said: "There is evidence
OL,13,Fthat the defendant had several motives
OL,14,Ffor attacking Mr Nouri, one of which
OL,15,Fwas also the reason why he killed Mr
OL,16,FCarney.
OL,18,F"First, there was some friction
OL,19,Fbetween the defendant and Mr Nouri
OL,20,Ffrom living in the shared house.
OL,26,@tD@TOUzD@AOU
