OL,7,F"He said he had wanted to kill them
OL,8,Fbecause of the conflict in Gaza and to
OL,9,Ffurther his desire that Palestine
OL,10,Fwould be free from the Zionists, by
OL,11,Fwhich he meant Israel.
OL,13,F"The defendant said he would have
OL,14,Fkilled more people if he had been able
OL,15,Fto do so."
OL,17,FHousemates noticed Alid was paying
OL,18,Fparticular attention to news coverage
OL,19,Fof the Hamas attacks on 7 October and
OL,20,Fhad begun to carry a knife, the jury
OL,21,Fheard.
