OL,7,FAt 5am on 13 October, he broke into
OL,8,Fhis housemate's bedroom armed with two
OL,9,Fknives.
OL,11,FThe jury heard a 999 call made by a
OL,12,Fhousemate in which shouts of "Allahu
OL,13,FAkbar" could be heard.
OL,15,FAlid stabbed him in the upper chest,
OL,16,Fnear his heart, causing Mr Nouri to
OL,17,Fscream "What are you doing?", the
OL,18,Fcourt heard.
