OL,7,FHe sustained further injuries to the
OL,8,Fmouth, thigh and calf while fighting
OL,9,Fhim off, and one of the attacker's
OL,10,Fknives snapped.
OL,12,FMr Nouri, who was bigger and stronger
OL,13,Fthan Alid, survived and the defendant
OL,14,Ffled.
OL,16,FAlid's path then crossed with Mr
OL,17,FCarney and CCTV images showed him
OL,18,Frepeatedly stab the pensioner in Tees
OL,19,FStreet at around 5.30am.
