OL,7,FFootage from a doorbell camera was
OL,8,Fplayed in court, during which the
OL,9,Fvictim was heard to cry out "no, no".
OL,11,FHe was able to get to his feet but
OL,12,Fcollapsed and died nearby, having been
OL,13,Fstabbed six times in the chest,
OL,14,Fabdomen and back.
OL,16,FAlid left Mr Carney for dead and was
OL,17,Farrested nearby with a bloody knife in
OL,18,Fhis waistband.
