OL,7,FIn custody at Middlesbrough police
OL,8,Fstation, Alid was recorded speaking in
OL,9,FArabic, saying "Allah willing, Gaza
OL,10,Fwould return to be an Arab country".
OL,12,FMr Sandiford said he went on "to
OL,13,Fpraise Allah and spoke of him being
OL,14,Fdispleased with those who went
OL,15,Fastray", of Palestine, and "that the
OL,16,FJews had divided the Arabs".
OL,18,FAlid said that if he had not injured
OL,19,Fhis hands "he would have continued
OL,20,Fwhat he referred to as 'the raid'", Mr
OL,21,FSandiford said.
