OL,7,FThe prosecution added: "The defendant
OL,8,Fspoke of returning with the army of
OL,9,FMuhammed with the non-believers having
OL,10,Fto pay tax to the Muslims and be
OL,11,Fhumbled."
OL,13,FIn his police interview, Alid admitted
OL,14,Fbeing responsible for the attempted
OL,15,Fmurder of Mr Nouri and the murder of
OL,16,FMr Carney and expressed the belief
OL,17,Fboth were dead, the prosecution said.
