OL,7,F"He said he had killed two adults
OL,8,Fbecause Israel had killed innocent
OL,9,Fchildren ` in other words he said he
OL,10,Fhad committed the attempted murder of
OL,11,FJaved Nouri and the murder of Mr
OL,12,FCarney in revenge for what he believed
OL,13,Fto be the killing of children by
OL,14,FIsrael.
OL,16,F"He swore by Allah that, if he had had
OL,17,Fa machine gun, and more weapons, he
OL,18,Fwould have killed more victims."
