OL,7,FMr Sandiford said Alid described Mr
OL,8,FCarney as an "innocent victim, killed
OL,9,Fbecause Britain had created the
OL,10,FZionist entity ` Israel ` and should
OL,11,Fmake it leave".
OL,13,FAlid told police: "They killed
OL,14,Fchildren and I killed an old man."
OL,16,FMr Sandiford said: "The defendant
OL,17,Fswore by Allah that if the
OL,18,Fcolonisation (by which he appeared to
OL,19,Fmean Israel) did not leave, Britain
OL,20,Fwas on the verge of an explosion and
OL,21,Fthere would be more victims.
