OL,7,F"The defendant swore by the greatness
OL,8,Fof Allah that Britain would be a wreck.
OL,10,F"The interview concluded with the
OL,11,Fdefendant swearing by Allah that he
OL,12,Fwas ready for Shahada ` martyrdom."
OL,14,FAlid, interviewed by DC Angela Harvey
OL,15,Fand DC Emma Stevenson, then became
OL,16,F"agitated" towards his interpreter, Mr
OL,17,FSandiford said.
